DAMAC has announced it will deliver over 8,800 luxury homes across Dubai in 2026, including projects such as DAMAC Hills, DAMAC Hills 2, DAMAC Lagoons, Chic Tower and Elegance Tower. The announcement was made by Managing Director Ali Sajwani.
The company also awarded more than AED 10 billion in construction contracts during the first half of 2026, highlighting its strong development pipeline and continued expansion across Dubai.
